angkok']::text[], 'ลูกชิ้นปลานายเงี๊ยบ พุทธมณฑลสาย4', 'Michelin Guide - Fish Ball Soup'),('hia wan khao tom pla', ARRAY['bangkok']::text[], 'Hia Wan Khao Tom Pla', 'Michelin Guide'),('rung rueang pork noodle left shop', ARRAY['bangkok']::text[], 'Rung Rueang Pork Noodle (Left Shop)', 'Michelin Guide - known for clear minced pork soup or the famous Tom Yam broth'),('baan yai phad thai', ARRAY['bangkok']::text[], 'Baan Yai Phad Thai', 'Michelin Guide'),('fried banana rama 5', ARRAY['bangkok']::text[], 'Fried Banana Rama 5', 'Michelin Guide'),('gen japanese charcoal grill', ARRAY['bangkok']::text[], 'Gen Japanese Charcoal Grill', 'Michelin Guide'),('here hai restaurant', ARRAY['bangkok']::text[], 'Here Hai Restaurant เฮียให้', 'Michelin Guide - known for seafood, large portions. Maybe more expensive than other streetfood.'),('arunwan', ARRAY['bangkok']::text[], 'Arunwan', 'Michelin Guide - Known for Pork offal and pickled cabbage soup'),('kuay jup mr jo', ARRAY['bangkok']::text[], 'Kuay Jup Mr. Jo', 'Michelin Guide - Known for pork skin that is crispy and surrounds rich layers of soft pork. Enjoy this dish as an entrée or mixed into a pepper broth and rice noodle soup known as Guay Jub'),('kintsugi by jeff ramsey', ARRAY['bangkok']::text[], 'Kintsugi by Jeff Ramsey', 'Michelin Guide'),('yamazato', ARRAY['bangkok']::text[], 'Yamazato', 'Michelin Guide'),('go ang pratu nam chicken rice', ARRAY['bangkok']::text[], 'Go-Ang Pratu Nam Chicken Rice', 'Michelin Guide - Chicken & Rice'),('thien duong baan dusit thani', ARRAY['bangkok']::text[], 'Thien Duong - Baan Dusit Thani', 'Michelin Guide - Viet'),('bangkok bold kitchen at central embassy', ARRAY['bangkok']::text[], 'Bangkok Bold Kitchen at Central Embassy', 'Michelin Guide - Word-of-mouth inspired Chef Nhoi to take the leap from cooking studio in the old town to opening a restaurant in the city centre. Her aim is to preserve the heritage of Thai taste that’s ‘basic and bold’ with creative twists. Check out the unique stir-fried pork and shrimp, hummingbird flowers, fish sauce and scrambled eggs. And the spicy salted beef in coconut cream is tender with balanced flavours, enlivened by fresh shallots and bird''s eye chillies.'),('kimpo khao tom pla', ARRAY['bangkok']::text[], 'Kimpo Khao Tom Pla', 'Michelin Guide'),('sanguan sri', ARRAY['bangkok']::text[], 'Sanguan Sri', 'Michelin Guide - Known for stir-fried crispy snake-head fish in red curry has a luscious amalgam of salty, sweet and spicy, with kaffir lime julienne adding acidity'),('tang jai yang fork roasting', ARRAY['bangkok']::text[], 'Tang Jai Yang (Fork Roasting)', 'Michelin Guide - Cantonese-style barbecue pork'),('somsak pu ob charoen rat', ARRAY['bangkok']::text[], 'Somsak Pu Ob (Charoen Rat)', 'Michelin Guide - This cart serves some of the best cheap steamed crabs or prawns on glass noodles'),('sawang noodles shop', ARRAY['bangkok']::text[], 'Sawang Noodles Shop 陈牛记云吞面', 'Michelin Guide - Known for crab claws, cash only.'),('kha mu charoensang silom', ARRAY['bangkok']::text[], 'Kha Mu Charoensang Silom', 'Michelin Guide - known for soft, caramelised pork stewed in a rich, aromatic gravy with Chinese herbs'),('tarn thong coconut custard', ARRAY['bangkok']::text[], 'Tarn Thong Coconut Custard', 'Michelin Guide'),('jok prince', ARRAY['bangkok']::text[], 'Jok Prince', 'Michelin Guide - known for congee'),('chakki', ARRAY['bangkok']::text[], 'Chakki', 'Michelin Guide - Chakki’s owner doesn’t believe in menus – everyone is here for their famous deep-fried wontons or deep-fried rice noodles and beef topped with gravy'),('guay jub ouan pochana', ARRAY['bangkok']::text[], 'Guay Jub Ouan Pochana', 'Michelin Guide known for Guay Jub (rolled rice noodle soup)'),('lim lao ngow fishball noodle', ARRAY['bangkok']::text[], 'Lim Lao Ngow Fishball Noodle', 'Michelin Guide - Known for homemade fish balls with Chinese-style noodles and fish wontons'),('bok kia thadindaeng', ARRAY['bangkok']::text[], 'Bok Kia Thadindaeng', 'Michelin Guide - 